-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/Can-private-aid-eradicate-poverty.pdf\">Can private aid eradicate poverty<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/How-can-we-optimize-the-use-of-public-funds-to.pdf\">How can we optimize the use of public funds to<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/Innovative-financing-for-development.pdf\">Innovative financing for development<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\">\u00a0<a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/Innovative-financial-solutions-to-scale-up-social-businesses.pdf\">Innovative financial solutions to scale up social businesses<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\">\u00a0<a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/Investing-in-social-enterprises1.pdf\">Investing in social enterprises<\/a> <\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.convergences.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/11\/Microfinance-and